(11, 'Marathon Plus AR', '<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Atap genteng Shingles Bitumen/Sirap Bitumen IKO Marathon AR Plus dengan berbahan dasar fiberglass dan aspal</span><br style=\"color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\" />\r\n	<br style=\"color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\" />\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Mengapa harus IKO Marathon AR Plus&nbsp; ?&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&bull; Fiberglass asphalt shingles.</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&bull; Traditional 3-Tab design.</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&bull; Tear strength values which exceed ASTM 03462 standards.</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&bull; &nbsp;F.M. tested Class &quot;A&quot; Fire Resistance Rating.</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&bull; Daya tahan angin hingga <span class=\"wpcf-field-value wpcf-field-textfield-value wpcf-field-wind-resistance-warranty-value\">97 km/h </span></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&bull; Garansi 25 tahun .</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&bull; 5 tahun IKO &quot;Iron Clad&quot; protection.</span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&bull; Algae Resistant.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"padding-left:20px\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"padding-left:20px\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Color Palette Marathon\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/color-palette-marathon-2020.jpeg\" style=\"width: 643px; height: 363px;\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"padding-left:20px\">\r\n	more info : <a href=\"https://www.iko.com/na/residential-roofing-shingles/three-t