(13, 'Dinasty', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	IKO Dinasty dengan Armourzone adalah shingle yang sangat kuat terhadap terpaan angin kencang</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Keuntungan memilih IKO Dinasty :<br />\r\n	- Tahan terhadap terpaan angin<br />\r\n	- Dilengkapi dengan IKO Armourzone<br />\r\n	- 5-7/8&quot; exposure<br />\r\n	- Blue-Green algae resistant<br />\r\n	- High Definition Color</p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<img class=\"img-responsive\" height=\"200px\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/dinasty.jpg\" width=\"200px\" /></center>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	IKO Dinasty dirancang sedemikian rupa agar kuat dari terpaan angin kencang hingga 210 KM/Jam dengan penggunaan hanya 4 paku IKO. Teknologi pencampuran warna menghasilkan warna yang berkualitas tinggi, menjadikan tampilan IKO Dinasty yang luar biasa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"padding-left:20px\">\r\n	<img alt=\"color palette dinasty\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/color-palette-dinasty-2020.jpeg\" style=\"width: 643px; height: 318px;\" /></div>\r\n', '<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial;\">\r\n	<strong>Wind-Resistance and &nbsp;Fast Installation Nailed.</strong></p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify;\" times=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial;\">IKO Dynasty with ArmourZone performance laminate shingles give you full coverage, lowering job costs associated with extra bundles and the labor to install them. &nbsp; These oversized shingles are heavy-duty and are installed with a 5 7/8&rdquo; exposure. Their special 1-1/4&rdquo; reinforced nailing area (the ArmourZone) ensures incredible fastening power. They&rsquo;ll help resist nail pull-through even at high winds and carry a 130 mph (210 km/h) wind limited warranty&sup1; with the use of only four nails. </span></span></p>\r\n<center>\r\n	<img class=\"img-responsive\" height=\"200px\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/dinasty.jpg\" width=\"200px\" /></center>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify;\" times=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial;\">IKO&rsquo;s special Fastlock&trade; sealant also helps resist water penetration and guards against wind uplift. &nbsp; IKO&rsquo;s advanced color blending technology creates distinctive hi-def colors that will &nbsp;make a home harmonize with its surroundings or truly stand out. &nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p open=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" text-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">IKO&rsquo;s Dynasty&trade;&nbsp;premium laminated architectural shingles offer protection from inclement weather and peace-of-mind. PLUS they look fantastic, boost curb appeal and can potentially increase the resale value of your property.</span></p>\r\n<p open=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" text-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Deep shadow bands add contrast and dimensional profile to give your roof a stunning, impressive appearance and roofline.</span></p>\r\n<p open=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" text-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Dynasty&trade; shingles with ArmourZone are manufactured in IKO&rsquo;s special &ldquo;Advantage&rdquo; size. Bigger than most competitors&rsquo; comparable product, they offer greater exposure to give you a dramatic-looking roof that really stands out from the ordinary.</span></p>\r\n<p open=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \" text-align:=\"\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Choose from 11 fresh, bold color blends. IKO&rsquo;s Color Blend Technology offers the perfect match for your home&rsquo;s architecture and your personal sense of style from rustic to urban, traditional to modern. Co-ordinated hip and ridge cap shingles are the ultimate accessory to create a spectacular new roofscape for your home.</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"padding-left:20px\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Color Palette Dinasty\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/color-palette-dinasty-2020.jpeg\" style=\"width: 643px; height: 318px;\" /></div>\r\n', '<ul bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Underlayer\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li>\r\n				Under layer&nbsp;armourbase pro 1 mm 20-85 dimensi 1x30m&nbsp;</li>\r\n			<li>\r\n				polygum 3 mm 5-15 dimensi X10&nbsp;</li>\r\n			<li>\r\n				Underlayer stormtite 1 mm 20-85 dimensi 76,2 X 1,219m&nbsp;</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		IKO starter Leading Edge Plus</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		paku IKO Galvanized (Dus)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Lem IKO (coverage 10 m&#39;/tube)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Flashing 9-12 mm untuk tepi atap (eff. 1,1 m/pc)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Wall Flashing untuk pertemuan dinding (eff. 0,9 m/pc)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Ridge Ventilator</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Hip and Ridge</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Multipleks</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Screw Multipleks (Dus)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \