(16, 'Armourshake', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Mengapa memilih IKO Armourshake ?</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	- Hi-Def Colors<br />\r\n	- Class A Fire Resistance Rating<br />\r\n	- Fast lock sealant<br />\r\n	- IKO Advantage Size<br />\r\n	-&nbsp;Blue-Green Algae Resistant</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	IKO Armourshake memiliki tampilan yang menyerupai kayu dengan warna kualitas tinggi. Didesain agar kuat terhadap terpaan angin, hujan maupun cuaca ekstrim lain nya. IKO Armourshake tersedia dalam IKO&#39;s Advantage size yaitu ukuran 5 1/2 eksposur atau 70 shingle per m<sup>2</sup>, dimana kompetitor lain memiliki rentang 90 shingle hingga 90 shingle per m<sup>2</sup>&nbsp;sehingga penggunaan IKO Armourshake menjadi lebih hemat 20%.<br />\r\n	IKO Armourshake menghemat waktu serta uang karena jauh lebih cepat dan lebih mudah untuk dipasang.<br />\r\n	Tersedia dalam berbagai warna yaitu Greystone, Chalet Wood,Western Redwood , Wheater stone atau Shadow Black.</p>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"padding-left:20px\">\r\n	<a data-gallery=\"example-gallery\" data-title=\"Armourshake - ChaletWood\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Armourshake-ChaletWood.jpg\"><img height=\"70px\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Armourshake-ChaletWood.jpg\" title=\"Chalet Wood\" width=\"70px\" /> </a> <a data-gallery=\"example-gallery\" data-title=\"Armourshake - Greystone\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Armourshake-Greystone.jpg\"> <img height=\"70px\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Armourshake-Greystone.jpg\" title=\"Greystone\" width=\"70px\" /> </a> <a data-gallery=\"example-gallery\" data-title=\"Armourshake - ShadowBlack\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Armourshake-ShadowBlack.jpg\"> <img height=\"70px\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Armourshake-ShadowBlack.jpg\" title=\"Shadow Black\" width=\"70px\" /> </a> <a data-gallery=\"example-gallery\" data-title=\"Armourshake - WeatheredStone\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Armourshake-WeatheredStone.jpg\"> <img height=\"70px\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Armourshake-WeatheredStone.jpg\" title=\"Weathered Stone\" width=\"70px\" /> </a> <a data-gallery=\"example-gallery\" data-title=\"Armourshake - WesternRedWood\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Armourshake-WesternRedWood.jpg\"> <img height=\"70px\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Armourshake-WesternRedWood.jpg\" title=\"Western RedWood\" width=\"70px\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"padding-left:20px\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	more info : <a href=\"https://www.armoroof.com/roofing-shingles/premium-designer-shingles/armourshake/\" target=\"_blank\">Armoroof</a></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	IKO Armourshake premium designer asphalt roofing shingles offer similar subtle color gradations, intricate profile and luxurious look of hand-hewn, random-cut cedar wood shakes at a much more reasonable cost. Manufactured with deep cuts and advanced color-blending technology, these high-quality, laminated shingles mimic the in-demand look of genuine wood shakes without the expense of their annual maintenance.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; tex