(17, 'Crowne Slate', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	IKO Crowne Slate merupakan produk dari IKO yang melambangkan Kualitas, Ketahanan, dan Inovasi</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Mengapa memilih IKO Crowne Slate&nbsp;?</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	- High Definition Colors<br />\r\n	- 10&quot; Exposure<br />\r\n	-&nbsp;Class 4 Impact Resistance Rating<br />\r\n	-&nbsp;Blue-Green Algae Resistant<br />\r\n	- Tahan terhadap&nbsp;Sinar Ultraviolet<br />\r\n	- Tahan terhadap angin, hujan maupun cuaca ekstrim lain nya</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	IKO Crowne Slate Premium Laminate Shingle didesain dengan&nbsp;teknologi pencampuran warna sehingga menghasilkan tampilan sirap batu yang natural.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	IKO Crowne Slate tersedia dalam 2 Warna Regal Stone dan Royal granite yang natural &nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"padding-left:20px\">\r\n	<a data-gallery=\"example-gallery\" data-title=\"Crowne Slate - Regal Stone\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/CrowneSlate-RegalStone.jpg\"><img height=\"70px\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/CrowneSlate-RegalStone.jpg\" title=\"Regal Stone\" width=\"70px\" /> </a> <a data-gallery=\"example-gallery\" data-title=\"Crowne Slate - Royal Granit\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/CrowneSlate-RoyalGranit.jpg\"> <img height=\"70px\" src=\"http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/CrowneSlate-RoyalGranit.jpg\" title=\"Royal Granite\" width=