(18, 'Enertherm ALU Insulation', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	IKO Enerthem ALU adalah lembaran insulasi yang terbuat dari polyisocyanurate foam 100% bebas CFC, HCFC, dan HFC dan dilapisi dengan multilayer gastight alumunium.</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	penggunaan :</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	a &nbsp;Insulasi pada atap datar baik atap&nbsp;kayu, beton maupun atap baja<br />\r\n	b &nbsp;Insulasi pada lantai<br />\r\n	c&nbsp; Insulasi pada dinding<br />\r\n	d &nbsp;Insulasi untuk dinding luar<br />\r\n	e &nbsp;Attic insulation</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Kelebihan IKO Enertherm :</p>\r\n<ul bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		CFC/HCFC free (Zero Ozone Depletion)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Fire-performance polyisocyanurate foam core</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Cocok untuk&nbsp;self-adhesive dan sistem membran waterproofing mechanically fastened</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Ringan dan mudah &nbsp;digunakan</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Insulasi yang luar biasa (thermal conductivity 0.023W/mK)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Tahan lama dan tidak memerlukan perawatan</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Tersedia juga tipe Tapered / cut-to-falls</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	more info :&nbsp;<a data-mce-=\"\" href=\"http://www.enertherm.eu/en-uk/\">IKO enertherm</a></p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3zfh3_hnEJwRTk4WjFlSENMUDA/view?usp=share_link&amp;resourcekey=0-VGdZrVMtcoC97C7tVJF64A\">Brosur</a></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Lato, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">IKO enertherm ALU is a 100% CFC, HCFC and HFC-free insulation board with a core of hard polyisocyanurate foam, coated on both sides with a multi-layer gastight aluminium complex.</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">IKO Enertherm insulation has the highest efficiency per m2. In other words: IKO enertherm insulates better with a thinner board. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">And that benefits not only you, but also the environment. The use of highly efficient insulation saves energy and thus decreases CO2 emissions. IKO enertherm is suitable for diverse applications. Enertherm PIR insulation boards have a global warming potential of zero.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">For Further Information</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><a href=\"http://www.enertherm.eu/\" style=\"outline: none; cursor: pointer; border: none; text-decoration-line: none;\">www.enertherm.eu</a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3zfh3_hnEJwRTk4WjFlSENMUDA/view?usp=share_link&amp;resourcekey=0-VGdZrVMtcoC97C7tVJF64A\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;\">Brosur</a></p>\r\n', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	a &nbsp;IKO range of PU adhesives</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	b &nbsp;IKO ALU tape 50 mm x 50 m</p>\r\n', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	a &nbsp;IKO range of PU adhesives</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	b &nbsp;IKO ALU tape 50 mm x 50 m</p>\r\n', '<table bitstream=\"\" border=\"1\" data-mce-selected=\"1\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				Board Size</td>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				1200mm x 1000mm (1.2m&sup2;)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				Standard Thicknesses</td>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				30mm/40mm/50mm/60mm/70mm/80mm/90mm/100mm/120mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					Thermal Conductivity</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					(Method BS EN 13165: 2001)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					0.023W/mK</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					Compressive Strength</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					(Method BS 4370: Part 1: 1988)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					120kPa (at yield of 10% compression)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					Water absorption</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					(24 hours in water at 20&deg;C)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					&nbsp;</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					0.5% by volume</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				Foam Density</td>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				32kg/m&sup3;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				Facings</td>\r\n			<td style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				Aluminium kraft complex<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', 'http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/01424-enertherm.jpg', '', '', 7, 1);
