(19, 'Spectraplan TPE', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	IKO Spectraplan TPE adalah penutup atap membrane jenis TPE (Themoplastic Polyolefin Elastomer) dengan bahan dasar Woven Polyester Scrim, Etilene Propilene Rubber dan Poliprofilen Metric dengan elastomer.</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	TPE memiliki 2 Tipe yaitu :</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	1. Spectraplan SM<br />\r\n	Sistem Pemasangan :<br />\r\n	- MFS (Mechanicall Fastened System)<br />\r\n	- Balasted System<br />\r\n	2. Spectraplan SG<br />\r\n	Sistem Pemasangan FAS (Fully Adhered System)</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	mengapa memilih TPE ?<br />\r\n	- Garansi 20 Tahun<br />\r\n	- Mudah dalam maintenance<br />\r\n	- Dapat dipasang / di welding dalam keadaan basah<br />\r\n	- Hasil welding homogen sehingga mengurangi resiko bocor pada area sambungan<br />\r\n	- Pemasangan aman karena tidak menghasilkan asap atau bahan kimia pada saat proses welding</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	TPE tersedia dalam warna Light Grey (RAL 7035) dan Dark Grey (RAL 7011)</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	informasi selengkapnya : <a href=\"https://www.ikopolymeric.com/spectraplan-single-ply-roofing-membrane/\">IKO Polymeric</a></p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3zfh3_hnEJwUFZiWkNnRzRsM28/view?usp=share_link&amp;resourcekey=0-sl_kRP6U3SL1Kf3dy-OJHg\">Brosur</a></p>\r\n