(21, 'Hydromax Siphonic Drainage', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<b>HydroMax&trade;</b>&nbsp;merupakan sebuah inovasi&nbsp; yang memanfaatkan kekuatan aliran air yang deras untuk menciptakan solusi sistem drainase atap yang berkualitas tinggi sehingga menjadikan Hydromax lebih baik daripada sistem drainase tradisional.<br />\r\n	Penggunaan pipa Hydromax lebih sedikit sehingga dapat menghemat waktu dan biaya. Hydromax dirancang sesuai standar internasional dan memiliki berbagai sertifikat seperti ASME A112.6.9 siphonic drain test, singapore standar SS 525 &nbsp;dan lain - lain.</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	beberapa keuntungan menggunakan hydromax :</p>\r\n<ul bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Penggunaan pipa down pipes lebih sedikit</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Pemasangan pipa secara horizontal tanpa kemiringan / Slope<b>&nbsp;&ndash; Flat Level</b>.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Low Maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Self Cleaning</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		High Performance Roof Drains</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Hydromax tersedia dalam berbagai ukuran dan dapat dipasang di berbagai jenis atap</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Desain pipa dirancang dengan software khusus sehingga lebih cepat, detail dan akurat</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Pemasangan pipa flexible</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Menggunakan bahan HDPE sehingga lebih kuat</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Segoe, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n	Siphonic Drainage offers&nbsp;a unique technology whereby you can achieve&nbsp;many&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Technical and Commercial Benefits.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Segoe, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n	Through the use of a siphonic roof drain to eliminate air ingress into the pipework, the horizontal pipes prime full of water which then accelerates down the vertical downpipe inducing a negative pressure flow - hence the siphonic or syphonic name.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 13px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana, Segoe, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline;\">\r\n	This results in high flow velocites that self cleanse the pipework and extremely efficiently removes the rainwater from the roof.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '<p bitstream=\"\" data-mce-style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\" font-size:=\"\" margin-bottom:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<strong><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\" style=\"font-family: Georgia, serif;\">50mm Balcony Pressurised Roof Drain</span></strong><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\" style=\"font-family: Georgia, serif;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span data-mce-style=\"font-family: \'Georgia\',serif; color: #333333;\" style=\"font-family: Georgia, serif;\">(laju air Max. = 1.5 l/d (Liter per detik) )</span></p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" data-mce-style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 