ast)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px; list-style: none;\">\r\n	8.Able to be used for large spans (up to &lt;24 meters)</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px; list-style: none;\">\r\n	9.Roof structure remained stable for the earthquake / vibrate</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px; list-style: none;\">\r\n	10.Anti-rust, mold, termites, and fire, as well as environmentally-friendly materials</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px; list-style: none;\">\r\n	11.Longer service life, so that prices become efficient and effective</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px; list-style: none;\">\r\n	12.Complete accessory to adjust to the shape of the roof</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px; list-style: none;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	More info :&nbsp;<a href=\"http://12truss.com/301-12-truss--rangka-baja-ringan.html\">Visit site</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1h3blO7X-YXo9nQ1iWwEyJacP4H8lzuRb/view?usp=share_link\">Brosur</a></p>\r\n', '<p bitstream=\"\" data-mce-style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<strong>Frame Truss</strong></p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" data-mce-style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', \'Bitstream Charter\', Times, serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; tex