(24, 'Kawa KZ Standing Seam', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	KAWA KZ standing seam merupakan sistem atap tanpa paku dengan desain tray yang lebar dan dapat digunakan pada desain atap minimal 1 derajat. Ukuran lembaran yang sangat panjang dapat disesuaikan dengan dibentuk di lapangan, akan mengurangi penumpukan sambungan dan kemungkinan bocor pada ujung sambungan</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Kelebihan KAWA KZ :</p>\r\n<ul bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Menggunakan sistem non-puncturing boltless roof .</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Menggunakan unique lock dan seam fastening&nbsp;sehingga 100% kedap air.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Atap Kawa KZ memiliki berat yang ringan tapi kuat.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Pemasangan yang cepat dan efisien</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Memungkinkan pembangunan sistem built-up direkayasa untuk panas maksimum dan isolasi suara.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Kedap Suara</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Mudah dikombinasikan dengan komponen atap lain</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Tahan karat karena penggunaan bahan-bahan seperti aluminium, baja COLORBOND Clean, tembaga dan stainless steel.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Presisi meruncing pada single pass</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Bentuknya yang melengkung &nbsp;meningkatkan estetika atap.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Info selengkapnya</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<a data-mce-=\"\" href=\"http://unitedseasons.com/portfolio/kawa-kz/\" target=\"_blank\">KAWA KZ</a></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	The&nbsp;<strong>KaWa</strong>&reg; KZ STANDING SEAM SERIES is a standing seam concealed roof fixing system. It can be uniquely rollformed by a proprietary process to precisely taper to exact angles and dimensions in a single pass. Each side lap is locked and seamed by a robotic seamer against strong winds and heavy rains. The wide tray design disperses water efficiently from the roof surface, even at a minimum roof pitch of 1 degree. Widths of 300 mm, 400 mm, 500 mm and 600 mm are available.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Advantages</strong>:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 15px; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 1em; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; list-style-position: initial !important; list-style-image: initial !important;\">\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px 0px 1em; list-style: disc !important; text-align: justify;\">\r\n		It is a non-puncturing boltless roof system.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px 0px 1em; list-style: disc !important; text-align: justify;\">\r\n		The unique lock and seam fastening ensures a 100% watertight roof.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px 0px 1em; list-style: disc !important; text-align: justify;\">\r\n		It is light in weight but yet strong.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px 0px 1em; list-style: disc !important; text-align: justify;\">\r\n		The system allows for quick and efficient installation.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px 0px 1em; list-style: disc !important; text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Allows the construction of engineered built-up system for maximum heat and sound insulation.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px 0px 1em; list-style: disc !important; text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Extremely durable against corrosion because of the usage of materials like aluminium, Clean COLORBOND&reg; steel, copper and stainless steel.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px 0px 1em; list-style: disc !important; text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Engineered to precisely taper in a single pass. Speeds up work and eliminates frequently encountered errors in the normally used antiquated multiple pass process.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em 0px 0px 1em; list-style: disc !important; text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Smooth curved to enhance the roof aesthetics.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	For Further Information</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<a data-mce-=\"\" href=\"http://unitedseasons.com/portfolio/kawa-kz/\" target=\"_blank\">KAWA KZ</a></p>\r\n', '<ul bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Box Gutter Central</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Gutter Gable</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Mono Ridge Flashing</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Halter and thermal pad</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Top Hat Support Bracket</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Tap Hat Sub-Purlin</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Ridge Capping</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Box Gutter Central</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Gutter Gable</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Mono Ridge Flashing</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Halter and thermal pad</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Top Hat Support Bracket</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Tap Hat Sub-Purlin</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Ridge Capping</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<strong>Technical Data</strong></p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font