22mm, 422mm, 522mm, 622mm &nbsp;Nominal 300mm, 400mm, 500mm, 600mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"style4\" scope=\"row\" style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				&nbsp;PROFILE HEIGHT</td>\r\n			<td class=\"style3\" style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				&nbsp;Nominal</td>\r\n			<td class=\"style3\" style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit;\">\r\n				65mm<br />\r\n				&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', 'http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/af1d4-bandara-sultan-hasanudin.jpg', '', '', 11, 1);
