(26, 'Firestone EPDM Geomembrane', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Firestone EPDM Geomembrane adalah rubber &nbsp;liner &nbsp;yang menawarkan solusi &nbsp;fleksibel dan tahan lama untuk berbagai pemasangan pada bidang&nbsp;pertanian, industri maupun&nbsp;komersial, termasuk:</p>\r\n<ul bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Danau Buatan dan sungai</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Irigasi dan danau buatan</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Penampungan air limbah</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Pertanian dan kolam ikan</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Fire reservoirs</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Settlement lagoons</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Telah digunakan hampir diseluruh dunia. Banyaknya permintaan yang disesuaikan dengan&nbsp;lingkungan - merupakan bukti kinerja yang luar biasa dari Firestone EPDM Geomembrane .</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Penggunaan pertama Firestone rubber membrane pada&nbsp;waduk irigasi yang terletak di selatan Spanyol dari hampir 40 tahun yang lalu. Hingga sekarang setelah beberapa dekade rubber liner terus memberikan solusi waterproofing yang dapat diandalkan.</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Keuntungan menggunakan geomembrane</p>\r\n<ul bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Sangat Flexibel bahkan pada suhu rendah</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Sangat elastis dan daya tarik yang kuat</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Kuat terhadap tekanan hydrostatis</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Mudah dipasang</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Kuat terhadap berbagai bahan kimia</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Ramah lingkungan</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Daya tahan untuk jangka panjang</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	The Firestone EPDM Geomembrane is an elastomeric membrane with a good combination of high elasticity and tensile strength. It is suitable for applications such as decorative ponds, water features, irrigation ponds and canals, dams, fire reservoirs, wastewater lagoons, landfill covers, animal waste containment.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	For Further Information</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.firestonebpe.com/lining.aspx\" style=\"outline: none; cursor: pointer; border: none; text-decoration-line: none;\">www.firestonebpe.com</a></p>\r\n', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<strong><u>T</u></strong><strong><u>h</u></strong><strong><u>i</u></strong><strong><u>c</u></strong><strong><u>k</u></strong><strong><u>nes</u></strong><strong><u>s</u></strong><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<u>Weight</u></strong></p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	1.02 mm (0.040&rdquo;)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1.32 kg/m2 &nbsp;(0.27 lb/ft2)</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	1.14 mm (0.045&rdquo;)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1.42 kg/m2 &nbsp;(0.29 lb/ft2)</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=