(27, 'Polygum ', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Polygum Roofing Membrane adalah waterproofing (lapisan kedap air) berbentuk membrane. Polygum dapat digunakan sebagai penutup &nbsp;atap - dak beton &nbsp;(screeding) atau sebagai waterproofing &nbsp;- roof garden, pondasi, dll</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	Keuntungan menggunakan polygum</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	&bull;Tri-laminate polyester composite reinforcement: stabilitas dimensi &lt;0,2%<br />\r\n	&bull; Turbo profiled underside<br />\r\n	&bull; Optimal joint security<br />\r\n	&bull; Flame contact surface 10% lebih baik dari torchons konvensional<br />\r\n	&bull; Fleksibel dengan detail rancangan bangunan &nbsp;yang sulit<br />\r\n	&bull; Rata-rata suhu dingin fleksibilitas mencapai - 25 &deg; C<br />\r\n	&bull; Turbo-profile yang unik<br />\r\n	&bull; aspal berkualitas APP Superior dengan ketahanan yang sangat baik<br />\r\n	&bull; UV-resistant<br />\r\n	&bull; panjang 7,5 meter/roll</p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3zfh3_hnEJwQlJRX19WaFh2ZGM/view?usp=share_link&amp;resourcekey=0-v4H3p-29oQlalJEpXN5kCA\">Brosur</a></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial; text-align: justify;\">Polygum&nbsp;</span>Roofing Membrane&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-family: Arial;\">is Waterproofing membrane, consisting of a non-woven polyester reinforcement, coated with plastomer bitumen.</span>Polygum membranes are manufactured to ISO 9000 and meet the following highly respected international standards and approvals</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	ULTIMATE IN COATING TECHNOLOGY</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	The Polygum range incorporates the ultimate standards both in APP and SBS coating technology. The special use of polymers and the absence of mineral fillers ensure a total waterproofing system perfectly adapted to the Irish climate. Mastery of both coating technologies enables the provision of an optimum waterproofing system for any given situation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	HIGHEST LIFE EXPECTANCY</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Polygum is designed to achieve only the highest mechanical performance and an unequalled life expectancy.The system has been in use for thirty years and the existence of roofs&nbsp;from that period, still in perfect condition, illustrate the proven performance of Polygum roofing over the last thirty years.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		HI-TEC GENERATION</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Conventional polyester&nbsp; carriers &nbsp;have &nbsp;an &nbsp;intrinsic &nbsp;bias towards relaxation in the roll width and a tightening in the roll length, which can in certain very unusual circumstances and specifications, when combined with a perfectly sealed sys- tem and an upward pressure, create a condition for minor ribbon blistering. The Polygum Hi-Tec generation of mem- branes are manufactured with a tri-laminate polyester / glass / polyester carrier, which is distinguished by its excep- tional dimensional stability in addition to its very robust tech- nical qualities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Benefit<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; Tri-laminate polyester composite reinforcement: dimensional stability &lt; 0,2%</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; Turbo profiled underside</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; Optimal joint security</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; Flame contact surface more than 10% better than conventional torchons</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; More flexible with difficult detail work</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; Average cold temperature flexibility - 25&deg;C</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; Unique Turbo-profile</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; Precision-aligned burn-away film</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; The burn-away film is carefully aligned with the edges of the roof membrane</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; Upper side with colorfast, imbedded slate granulation with perfect adherence</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; Superior quality APP bitumen with excellent resistance to ageing</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; UV-resistant</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&bull; 7.5 metre roll</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3zfh3_hnEJwQlJRX19WaFh2ZGM/view?usp=share_link&amp;resourcekey=0-v4H3p-29oQlalJEpXN5kCA\">Brosur</a></p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	<span bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">Aksesoris Primer digunakan untuk sistem torching, untuk aksesoris lain nya disesuaikan dengan sistem pemasangan</span></p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	<span bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">Aksesoris Primer digunakan untuk sistem torching, untuk aksesoris lain nya disesuaikan dengan sistem pemasangan</span></p>\r\n', '<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<strong data-mce-style=\"font-weight: bold !important;\">Technical Data</strong></p>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<strong data-mce-style=\"font-weight: bold !important;\">TYPES</strong></p>\r\n<ul bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Polygum AE Plain 3mm</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Polygum AE Plain 4mm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p bitstream=\"\" font-size:=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, \" times=\"\">\r\n	<strong data-mce-style=\"font-