(33, 'Firestone Polyiso Insulation', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Firestone Polyiso 95+ GL adalah insulasi dari Amerika berbentuk lembaran yang dilapisi dengan glass reinforced mat facer pada kedua sisinya. Tidak merusak lapisan ozon karena bebas HCFC. Polyiso terdiri dari bahan dasar Polyisocianurate foam, glass reinforced mat facer. Cocok dengan berbagai desain atap, ringan, mudah dipasang dan dapat dipasang pada atap metal, beton atau kayu.&nbsp;Tidak hanya mudah dipasang, Polyiso juga tahan terhadap api dan angin serta memberikan perlindungan pada permukaan atap anda.&nbsp;<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	keuntungan dengan menggunakan insulasi Firestone Polyiso :</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	- Kompatibel dengan sistem ballasted, fully adhered dan mechanically attached single-ply systems.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- Juga tersedia flat board dengan ukuran 1,22 m x 2,25m dan ketebalan dari&nbsp; 25,4 mm hingga 101,6 mm</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- Coated and perforated glass reinforced mat facer of approx. 150 g/m2&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	- Firestone EPDM and TPO Roofing systems installed over firestone ISO 95+ GL Obtain BROOF(t1) fire rating.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\r\n', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Firestone offers two types of Polyisocyanurate boards: Firestone ISO 95+ GL insulation board and Firestone ISOGARD<sup>TM</sup> HD Cover Board. Thanks to their physical properties, they bring added value to the roofing system, prior to installation of a durable EPDM or TPO roofing membrane.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	The <strong>Firestone ISO 95+ GL</strong> Insulation board offers high-energy efficiency for which PIR boards are renowned. Compatible with all types of commercial roofing systems, this lightweight, easy-to-handle insulation is suited for direct applicatiion on to steel roof. concrete or wood deck. It provides outstanding thermal resistance, dimensional and compressive strength<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>Firestone ISOGARD<sup>TM</sup> HD </strong>is a high density cover board that not only combines high impact resistane and ease of installtion in a single durable product, but also enchanes fire and wind resistance of the roof build up, adds compressive strength to the entire roof system and provides a smooth surface in case of reroofing. With a high compressive strenght and a superior resistance to extreme weather conditions, ISOGARD<sup>TM&nbsp;</sup>HD provides an added measur of protection for any roof</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Technical Feature<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	- Compatible with ballasted, fully adhered and mechanically attached single-ply systems.<br />\r\n	- Available in flat boards of 1,22 m x 2,25m and in thicknesses ranging from 25,4 mm to 101,6 mm<br />\r\n	- Coated and perforated glass reinforced mat facer of approx. 150 g/m<sup>2 </sup><br />\r\n	- Firestone EPDM and TPO Roofing systems installed over firestone ISO 95+ GL Obtain B<sup>ROOF</sup>(t1) fire rating.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Contact the firestone technical department for further information</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n	<table class=\"table table-striped\" width=\"100%\">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;Property</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;ASTM Test</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					Typical Value</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;EN Test</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					Typical Value</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;Density</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;D-1622</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;32 kg/m<sup>3</sup></td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp; 823</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;32 kg/m<sup>3</sup></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;Compressive&nbsp; &nbsp;Strength</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;D-1621</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;&gt; 138 kPa</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;&nbsp;826</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;&gt; 138 kPa</td>\r\n