\n					&nbsp;&lt; 3 % (by volume)</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;Service Temperature</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;-73<sup>o&nbsp;</sup>to 121<sup>o&nbsp;</sup>C</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	a. Mechanical Attached System</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	b. Fully Adhered System</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	c. Ballasted System</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	a. Mechanical Attached System</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	b. Fully Adhered System</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	c. Ballasted System</p>\r\n', 'http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/Firestone_Polyiso2-555.jpg', '', '', NULL, 0),
(34, 'Aquapanel Cement Board Outdoor', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	AQUAPANEL&reg; Cement Board Outdoor ex. Jerman merupakan cement board yang 100% tahan terhadap air dan dapat dilengkungkan dengan radius minimal 3 meter. Terbuat dari bahan semen portland, agregat dan dilapisi dengan fibermesh pada seluruh permukaannya. Untuk mengoptimalkan kedap suara, pemasangan bisa dengan menambahkan insulation.Terbuat dari bahan anorganik sehingga tahan terhadap kondisi cuaca yang ekstrem sekalipun. Meskipun ringan dan kuat, AQUAPANEL&reg; Cement Board Outdoor sangat Fleksibel sehingga dapat dilengkungkan mengikuti bentuk dinding.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Keuntungan :</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div>\r\n			100% tahan air</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Tahan di segala jenis cuaca yang sangat extrim</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Tidak akan menggelembung</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Tahan terhadap jamur dan kelembaban</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Kuat(tahan terhadap benturan)</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Bahan yang di gunakan sangat aman dan higienis</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Tidak mudah terbakar dan tergolong kedalam kelas A1</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Dapat menahan beban 50kg/m2</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Dapat mereduksi suara hingga 60 db</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<div>\r\n			Pemotongan hanya menggunakan cutter</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div>\r\n	<a href=\"https://www.aquapanel.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Aquapanel Website</a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3zfh3_hnEJwNnpYdnMwNFhyWTA/view?usp=share_link&amp;resourcekey=0-ULOiW17rG-NHotv7LgkhBw\">Brosur</a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	AQUAPANEL&reg; Cement Board Outdoor is an innovative way to build exterior walls and fa&ccedil;ades. The board is the ideal exterior render substrate and can be used for many other surface finishes, such as paint or brick slips. It is a robust, non-combustible building panel and helps to form equally strong but significantly thinner structures, which provides more interior space in buildings.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	AQUAPANEL&reg; Cement Board Outdoor is made entirely from inorganic materials and withstands even extreme weather conditions. Its flexibility allows the board to be curved, making it a highly versatile building solution.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	PRODUCT FEATURES AND BENEFITS</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Strong but still lightweight, AQUAPANEL&reg; Cement Board Outdoor is a future-proof building material. Besides its strength and low weight, there are multiple other benefits for architects, contractors, and building users alike :</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>\r\n			100% water-resistant</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			No deterioration, swelling or loss of stability</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Resistant to moisture, weathering, mould, and mildew</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Freeze-thaw cycle proven</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Stable and durable Portland cement construction</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Board can be curved</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Safe and hygienic material</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Non-combustible</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Strong, robust, and highly impact-resistant</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<a href=\"https://www.aquapanel.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Aquapanel Website</a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3zfh3_hnEJwNnpYdnMwNFhyWTA/view?usp=share_link&amp;resourcekey=0-ULOiW17rG-NHotv7LgkhBw\">Brosur</a></div>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Screw Needle</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Screw Bord</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Tyvek</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Joint Filler</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Aquapanel tape</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Basecoat</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Reinforcing Mesh</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Basecoat Primer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Screw Needle</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Screw Bord</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Tyvek</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Joint Filler</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Aquapanel tape</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Basecoat</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Reinforcing Mesh</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Basecoat Primer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<table class=\"table table-striped\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Lebar (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1200 / 900</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Panjang (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1200 / 2400 / 2500 / 2800&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Tebal (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				12,5</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Berat (kg/m<sup>2</sup>)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				approx. 16</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Min. lengkung radius&nbsp;(m) untuk 1200 mm wide board</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				3</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Min. lengkung radius&nbsp;(m) untuk&nbsp; 300 mm wide strip</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<table class=\"table table-striped\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Width (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1200 / 900</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Height (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1200 / 2400 / 2500 / 2800&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Thickness (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				12,5</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Weight (kg/m<sup>2</sup>)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				approx. 16</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Min.&nbsp;curved radius (m) for 1200 mm wide board</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				3</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Min. curved radius&nbsp;(m) for 300 mm wide strip</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\