(35, 'Aquapanel Cement Board Indoor', '<div style=\"text-align: justify; \">\r\n	AQUAPANEL&reg; Cement Board Indoor ex. Jerman merupakan bahan bangunan pengganti dinding pada konstruksi dinding yang sangat tahan terhadap cuaca ekstrim, dapat diandalkan dan stabil terhadap kondisi basah dan lembab.&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diproduksi dari bahan anorganik yang sangat tahan terhadap air, AQUAPANEL&reg; Cement Board Indoor sangat ringan, sehingga mudah dipasang dengan cepat serta fleksible. </span>Untuk mengoptimalkan kedap suara pemasangan&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;AQUAPANEL&reg; Cement Board&nbsp;</span>bisa dengan menambahkan insulasi.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Keuntungan yang anda dapatkan dari AQUAPANEL&reg;&nbsp;Cement Board&nbsp;&nbsp;:</p>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>\r\n			100% tahan air</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Tahan di segala jenis cuaca yang sangat extrim</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Tidak akan menggelembung</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Tahan terhadap jamur dan kelembaban</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Kuat(tahan terhadap benturan)</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Bahan yang di gunakan sangat aman dan higienis</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Tidak mudah terbakar dan tergolong kedalam kelas A1</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Dapat menahan beban 50kg/m2</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Dapat mereduksi suara hingga 60 db</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Pemotongan hanya menggunakan cutter</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Pemasangan menjadi lebih cepat</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Perbaikan mudah dan cepat</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	More Info :&nbsp; <a href=\"https://www.aquapanel.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Aquapanel Website</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3zfh3_hnEJwc1pTbGEyamFqalE/view?usp=share_link&amp;resourcekey=0-Hs6zunO2v4Sf3zlJgKiW3A\">Brosur</a></p>\r\n', '<div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		As a modern drylining technology, AQUAPANEL&reg; Cement Board Indoor is the perfect board for exceptionally light performance, reliability, and stability even in the most challenging wet and humid conditions for both wall and ceiling applications &ndash; making it ideal for everything from swimming pools and steam saunas to communal showers and kitchen areas.</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n	<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Manufactured from inorganic materials and highly resistant to water and mould, AQUAPANEL&reg; Cement Board Indoor is a real lightweight &ndash; making it easy to handle and fast to install, with superb flexibility for curved walls, too. Its surface offers the basis for a multitude of design options, comprising finishes in all quality grades.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Benefit :</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		100% water-resistant</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Mould and mildew-resistant</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Non-combustible (A1) &ndash; complies with European standards</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Robust and reliable with high impact resistance and sound insulation</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Safe to use, hygienic, and manufactured from sustainable materials</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Only 11 kg/m2 &ndash; for less effort in handling and overhead installation</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Easy to cut using a simple score-and-snap technique</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		No pre-drilling required</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Bending radius of 1 m at full board size for curved constructions</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Ready keyed for tiling &ndash; only one layer required for tile finish</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Supports tiling up to 50 kg/m2</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Surface qualities up to Q4-level can be achieved</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	More Info :&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aquapanel.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Aquapanel Website</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B3zfh3_hnEJwc1pTbGEyamFqalE/view?usp=share_link&amp;resourcekey=0-Hs6zunO2v4Sf3zlJgKiW3A\">Brosur</a></p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL Maxi Screws</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL Exterior Tape</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL interior primer</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL exterior basecoat</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL joint adhesive (PU)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL Q4 Finish</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL Maxi Screws</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL Exterior Tape</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL interior primer</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL exterior basecoat</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL joint adhesive (PU)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		AQUAPANEL Q4 Finish</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<table class=\"table table-striped\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Lebar (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1200 / 900</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Panjang (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1200 / 2400 / 2500 / 2800&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Tebal (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				12,5</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Berat (kg/m<sup>2</sup>)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				approx. 16</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Min. lengkung radius&nbsp;(m) untuk 1200 mm wide board</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				3</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Min. lengkung radius&nbsp;(m) untuk&nbsp; 300 mm wide strip</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<table class=\"table table-striped\" style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Width (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1200 / 900</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Height (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1200 / 2400 / 2500 / 2800&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Thickness (mm)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				12,5</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Weight (kg/m<sup>2</sup>)</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				approx. 16</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Min.&nbsp;curved radius (m) for 1200 mm wide board</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				3</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Min. curved radius&nbsp;(m) for 300 mm wide strip</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r