: 5px;\">\r\n					Mabey Universal</li>\r\n				<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition: all 0.3s; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; position: relative; padding-left: 5px;\">\r\n					Mabey Delta</li>\r\n				<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition: all 0.3s; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; position: relative; padding-left: 5px;\">\r\n					Mabey Atlas</li>\r\n				<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; transition: all 0.3s; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; position: relative; padding-left: 5px;\">\r\n					Mabey Logistic Support Bridge</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/mabey.jpg', '', '', NULL, 1),
(38, 'Firestone Pondgard', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Firestone Rubber PondGard Pond Liner<strong>&nbsp;</strong>adalah kinerja yang luar biasa tinggi 1.02m karet EPDM geomembrane direkayasa untuk aplikasi tugas domestik dan berat komersial dengan nama terkemuka di teknologi karet dan inovasi, komitmen Firestone BUILDING PRODUCTS.Firestone terhadap produk yang berkualitas dan mulai pelayanan di fasilitas manufaktur berbasis di Prescott, dan Kingstree, USA.They adalah tanaman pertama di industri membran karet untuk menerima sertifikasi ISO9002 dan ISO14001 yang merupakan bukti dari komitmen perusahaan untuk quaility dan pengelolaan lingkungan.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Untuk Informasi Lebih Lanjut</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.firestonebpe.com/lining.aspx\" href=\"http://www.firestonebpe.com/lining.aspx\">www.firestonebpe.com</a></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<fck:meta content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" http-equiv=\"Content-Type\"><fck:meta content=\"Word.Document\" name=\"ProgId\"><fck:meta content=\"Microsoft Word 12\" name=\"Generator\"><fck:meta content=\"Microsoft Word 12\" name=\"Originator\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span sans-serif=\"\" verdana=\"\">Firestone Rubber PondGard Pond Liner</span><span sans-serif=\"\" verdana=\"\">&nbsp;is an exceptional high performance 1.02m EPDM rubber geomembrane engineered for both domestic and&nbsp;heavy duty commercial applications by the premier name in rubber technology and innovation,&nbsp;</span><span sans-serif=\"\" verdana=\"\">FIRESTONE BUILDING PRODUCTS</span><span sans-serif=\"\" verdana=\"\">.Firestone&#39;s commitment to quality products and services starts at its manufacturing facilities based in Prescott,and Kingstree,USA.They were the first plants in the rubber membrane industry to receive ISO9002 and ISO14001 certification which are a testimony&nbsp;of the company&#39;s commitment to quaility and environmental management.</span></span></span>&nbsp;</fck:meta></fck:meta></fck:meta></fck:meta></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">For Further Information</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.firestonebpe.com/lining.aspx\" href=\"http://www.firestonebpe.com/lining.aspx\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">www.firestonebpe.com</span></a></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The Firestone Lining Systems uses a complete range of materials including the Firestone EPDM Geomembrane, adhesives, tape, sealant, cleaning products and prefabricated accesories in order to guarantee the homogeneity of the systems.</span></span><br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>For Further Information</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/TECH-DATA-SHEET%20GEOMEMBRANE.pdf\" href=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/TECH-DATA-SHEET%20GEOMEMBRANE.pdf\">Download Here</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/Technical%20Data%20EPDM%20Geomembrane%20-%201.pdf\" href=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/Technical%20Data%20EPDM%20Geomembrane%20-%201.pdf\">Download Here</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/Technical%20Data%20EPDM%20Geomembrane%20-%202.pdf\" href=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/Technical%20Data%20EPDM%20Geomembrane%20-%202.pdf\">Download Here</a></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Umum</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Furnish dan benar-benar menginstal Firestone EPDM Sistem Geomembrane sesuai dengan spesifikasi Firestone&#39;s diterbitkan dan detail.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>A. Panel Layout</strong><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Kontraktor instalasi harus menyediakan gambar panel layout atau rencana<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Rencana ini harus dibuat berdasarkan rincian spesifikasi dan desain, dan akan menunjukkan posisi lapisan panel dan lapangan<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Penempatan panel akan dilanjutkan sesuai dengan rencana ini kecuali perubahan harus dilakukan karena kondisi lokasi yang tidak terduga<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>B. Instalasi Details</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Kontraktor pemasang harus memberikan salinan dari setiap penghentian detail khusus yang mungkin diperlukan<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Untuk Informasi Lebih Lanjut</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/INSTAL-TOOLS%20firestone%20geomembrane.pdf\" href=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/INSTAL-TOOLS%20firestone%20geomembrane.pdf\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Klik Disini</span></span></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/Section%20II-%20EPDM%20Geomembrane%20Installation%20Guide%202.pdf\" href=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/Section%20II-%20EPDM%20Geomembrane%20Installation%20Guide%202.pdf\">Klik Disini</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/SYSTEM-INSTAL%20FIRESTONE%20GEOMEMBRANE.pdf\" href=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/SYSTEM-INSTAL%20FIRESTONE%20GEOMEMBRANE.pdf\">Klik Disini</a></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">General</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Furnish and completely install the Firestone EPDM Geomembrane System in accordance with Firestone&#39;s published specifications and detail.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Submittals</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>A. Panel Layout</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The installation contractor shall provide a panel layout drawing or plan</span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">This plan shall be made based on the specification and design details, and will indicate the position of the panel and field seams.</span></span></li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The placement of the panels will proceed according to this plan unless changes must be made due to unforeseen site conditions</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>B. Installation Details</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The installaton contractor shall provide copies of any special detail terminations that may be required</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">For Further Information</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/INSTAL-TOOLS%20firestone%20geomembrane.pdf\" href=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/INSTAL-TOOLS%20firestone%20geomembrane.pdf\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Download Here</span></span></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/Section%20II-%20EPDM%20Geomembrane%20Installation%20Guide%202.pdf\" href=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/Section%20II-%20EPDM%20Geomembrane%20Installation%20Guide%202.pdf\">Download Here</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<a _fcksavedurl=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/SYSTEM-INSTAL%20FIRESTONE%20GEOMEMBRANE.pdf\" href=\"http://www.roof-online.com/assets/Brosur%20Website/SYSTEM-INSTAL%20FIRESTONE%20GEOMEMBRANE.pdf\">Download Here</a></p>\r\n', '', '', '', NULL, 0);
