(50, 'Flexiroof', '<p>\r\n	FLEXIROOF Merupakan Genteng Metal Fleksibel yang bisa dikreasikan sesuai gaya atap rumah idamanmu. Bisa dipasang di Atap bentuk Cembung, Cekung,ataupun Gelombang. Flexi Roof juga bisa dipasang dengan2 pola yaiutu, Dynamic dan Minimalis tanpa tambahan Multiplek. Dengan begini, Flexi Roof bisa menjadikan rumah idaman anda semakin Cantik dan Keren.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	Keunggulan FLEXIROOF :</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Panjang bisa mengikuti pesanan, bias On Site Production</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Banyak pilihan warna</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Bentuk bisa Minimalis dan Dynamic</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Flexible mengikuti bentuk atap</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	Info selengkapnya : <a href=\"http://www.12truss.com/303-flexi-roof.html\">Visit site</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1oAxOa70jrGIhnd49J_ObaTGshRAFDQZo/view?usp=share_link\">Brosur</a></p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	More info :&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.12truss.com/303-flexi-roof.html\">Visit site</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1oAxOa70jrGIhnd49J_ObaTGshRAFDQZo/view?usp=share_link\">Brosur</a></p>\r\n', '', '', '<div>\r\n	Spesifikasi FLEXIROOF :</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Ketebalan 025 s/d 035 mm (Asli BMT)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Galvalum G300 eith Back Coating</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Sudah ber-SNI</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Profil lebih dalam</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Lebar 800 mm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<div>\r\n	Spesification FLEXIROOF :</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Thickneess 025 - 035 mm (BMT Original)</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Galvalum G300 eith Back Coating</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		SNI Certified</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Deeper profile</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Width 800 mm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', 'http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/flexiroof.jpg', '', '', 18, 1),
(51, 'Soprasun P3', '<div>\r\n	Soprasun P3 Adalah waterproofing membrane bakar berbahan dasar Plastomeric Modified Bitumen ( APP ),memilki lapisan Thermofusible Plastic Film pada permukaan bawah dan Natural Sand finish pada permukaan atas. Menggunakan Composite Reinfocerment yaitu combinasi antara Nonwoven Polyester Mesh dan Fiberglass</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Soprasun P3 memiliki karakteristik material yang flexible, kuat, tahan lama, dan tidak mudah sobek.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Info selengkapnya : <a href=\"https://soprema.com.au/product/soprasun-plus-3-1148/\">Soprema Soprasun</a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/15TZJ12iEJvmqwVDi2CZX_agUk4aq-tZO/view?usp=share_link\">Brosur</a></div>\r\n', '<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		Heat-welded base sheet membrane composed of a composite reinforcement and APP modified bitumen.</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<strong>Benefits</strong></div>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Excellent dimensional stability and elastic performance</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			Can be installed any time of the year, wide temperature tolerance</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	More info :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://soprema.com.au/product/soprasun-plus-3-1148/\">Soprema Soprasun</a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/15TZJ12iEJvmqwVDi2CZX_agUk4aq-tZO/view?usp=share_link\">Brosur</a></div>\r\n', '', '', '<div>\r\n	Dimensi</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Panjang<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: 10 M</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Lebar<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: 1 M</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Tebal <span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: 3 mm</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Bobot<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: 3,9 Kg/M&sup2;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Overlap<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: 10 cm</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Coverage<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: 8,91 M&sup2;/Roll</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Data Teknis</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Negara Asal<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: Belgia / ME</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Cara Pasang<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: Bakar ( Torch on )</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Suhu Toleran<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: -5&ordm;C sd 120&ordm;C</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Flexibilitas <span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: 45%</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Kuat Tarik<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>: 650 N/50mm</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Fungsi<span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span>:&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Waterproofing non ekspose</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	Base Sheet Waterproofing ( &gt;2 Ply ) <span style=\"white-space:pre\"> </span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '', '', '', 'http://roof-online.com/atl/assets/uploads/images/soprasun-soprema.jpeg', '', '', 4, 1),
(52, 'Soprema Tecsound', '<p>\r\n	High-density, polymer-based, asphalt-free synthetic soundproofing membrane, which is viscoelastic and highly adaptable, and provides good acoustic insulation in the different construction elements without increasing thickness.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Benefits :&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		High acoustic insulation</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Easy to handle and adaptable to uneven surface</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Act as a vapor control layer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	High-density, polymer-based, asphalt-free synthetic soundproofing membrane, which is viscoelastic and highly adaptable, and provides good acoustic insulation in the different construction elements without increasing thickness.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Benefits :&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		High acoustic insulation</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Easy to handle and adaptable to uneven surface</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Act as a vapor control layer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	Benefits :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		High acoustic insulation</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Easy to handle and adaptable to uneven surface</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Act as a vapor control layer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '<p>\r\n	<strong>Properties</strong></p>\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:500px;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Fungsi</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Soundproofing</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Product roles</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Soundproofing</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Unit</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Square meter (m<sup>2</sup>)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Conditioning</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Roll</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Data teknis</strong></p>\r\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:500px;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Panjang</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				6 m</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Lebar</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				1.22 mm</td>\r\